  <section>
    <h2>Browser Support</h2>
    <p>The <code>&lt;dialog&gt;</code> element is supported in all modern browsers.</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Invokers API:</strong> Chrome 135+, Edge 135+, Safari TP, Firefox Nightly. Use the <a href="https://github.com/keithamus/invokers-polyfill">invokers-polyfill</a> for broader support.</li>
      <li><strong>@starting-style:</strong> Chrome 117+, Safari 17.5+. Other browsers fall back to keyframe animations.</li>
      <li><strong>backdrop-filter:</strong> All modern browsers. The blur effect on the backdrop degrades gracefully.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
